USAID Commits $60 Million to Ghana’s Farmers, Graphic Says

-- B y   M o s e s   M o z a r t   D z a w u
-- 
2011-06-21T10:53:24Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-21/usaid-commits-60-million-to-ghana-s-farmers-graphic-says.html
The  U.S. Agency for International
Development  committed $60 million to the development of
agriculture in  Ghana ’s three northern regions, Daily Graphic
reported today.  The Accra-based newspaper cited a statement from the vice
president’s office that corrected a previous announcement that
gave the figure as $340 million.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Antony Sguazzin at 
 asguazzin@bloomberg.net . 